    "body": "I left a now-hidden comment, but an icky but hidden-from-the-user strategy for dealing with windows may be something like this:\n\n``````\n/// ```\n/// # foo();\n/// # #[cfg(windows)] fn foo() {}\n/// # #[cfg(unix)] fn foo() {\n/// ... dox dox dox\n///\n/// ... dox dox dox\n/// # }\n/// ```\n``````\n",
